# CODEOWNERS — role-based required reviewers.
#
# When a PR changes files under a path below, GitHub requires an approving
# review from that path's owner(s) (once branch protection has
# "Require review from Code Owners" enabled).
#
# IMPORTANT: every @name here must be a REAL GitHub account that is a
# collaborator with write access on this repo — otherwise GitHub ignores
# the line. (On a personal repo you cannot use teams like @org/devops;
# convert the repo to an Organization to use team handles instead.)

# ── DevOps: infrastructure, GitOps, and CI/CD ──────────────────────────
/infra/        @user-devops
/ArgoCD/       @user-devops
/.github/      @user-devops

# ── Developers: application source code ────────────────────────────────
/services/backend/    @user-developer1 @user-developer2
/services/frontend/   @user-developer1 @user-developer2

# ── QA: tests ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/services/tests/   @user-qa

# ── Default owner for everything else ──────────────────────────────────
*   @user-devops
